  "description": "<p>虽然处于两种完全不同的游戏元素，不过暴雪正试图将《暗黑破坏神3》其中的拍卖行等现金交易方式引入到《魔兽世界》中。日前在美国战网论坛上的这一消息引发了WOW玩家的热议，今天暴雪社区经理Zarhym正式发表回应称：“<strong>我们正积极探索全新的的支付方式，以确保玩家能够在不离开游戏的情况下直接在游戏 内部进行交易和购买操作。作为这个目标的一部分，我们会将有所有的资料和元素都放在PTR上。此外我们也会随时更新我们的开发进程和相关的研发计划。”</strong><br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e4695fc/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243695.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E6%AD%A3%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%8A%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243695.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E6%AD%A3%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%8A%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243695.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E6%AD%A3%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%8A%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243695.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%AA%E6%AD%A3%E8%80%83%E8%99%91%E4%B8%BA%E3%80%8A%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%80%8B%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedspo